---
title: Easy Ground Chicken Ragu with Spaghetti
description: Using ground chicken makes this Bolognese-inspired dinner just a bit lighter than its beefy counterpart. Full of hidden veggies and served on tender pasta, this dish will please even the pickiest eaters!
